Install Plugins
→ Plugins → Manage and Install Plugins
→ Go to Not Installed tab
→ Install OpenLayers and OSM Place Search plugins.

Activate OSM Place Search Panel
→ If not visible, go to View → Panels
→ Enable OSM Place Search.

Add Open Street Map Layer
→ Web → OpenLayers Plugin → Open Street Map.

Search for a Place
→ In OSM Place Search panel, type Mumbai (or any place).
→ Double-click the result or click and press to zoom to the location.
